title: FOUR-STAR Admirals & NETFLIX WALKOUTS! Welcome to the Trans World Order!
description:
A new four-star admiral has been sworn in. It's transgender assistant health secretary Rachel Levine. We'll explain how and why and the issue with people calling Levine a "female.” There was also a Netflix “walkout” over Dave Chappelle. Well, kind of. We also debunk Pete Buttigieg's ridiculous claims that the supply chain is just fine.
